<subSubSection id="C30B26F8647FFFE08BAE48CEFB1A1310" pageId="15" pageNumber="52" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BAE7573647FFFE08BAE48CEFEDC12A0" blockId="15.[151,649,151,214]" box="[151,313,187,214]" pageId="15" pageNumber="52">
<figureCitation id="132A69F6647FFFE08BAE48CEFEDC12A0" box="[151,313,187,214]" captionStart="FIGURES 21–27" captionStartId="14.[151,264,1872,1896]" captionTargetBox="[161,1424,192,1838]" captionTargetId="figure-21@14.[151,1436,181,1849]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURES 21–27. Pericoma estrelica spec. nov.: 21 terminalia ventral view; 22 wing. Heteroberdeniella jaramensis: 23 styles, aedeagus and hypandrium; 24 aedeagus. H. guadarramica sp. nov.: 25 wing; 26 styles, aedeagus, and hypandrium; 27 epandrium with appendages and hypoproct. Scale bars: Figs 22, 25—1 mm; figs 21, 23, 24, 26, 27—0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6488102" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6488102/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="52">Figures 25–27</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BAE7573647FFFE08BAE4976FB1A1310" blockId="15.[151,1437,259,1186]" pageId="15" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis id="B965A961647FFFE08BAE4976FEEE136B" bold="true" box="[151,267,259,285]" pageId="15" pageNumber="52">Diagnose.</emphasis>
A 
<taxonomicName id="4C110EF0647FFFE08A0B4976FE51136B" authorityName="Vaillant" authorityYear="1976" box="[306,436,259,285]" class="Insecta" family="Psychodidae" genus="Berdeniella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B965A961647FFFE08A0B4976FE51136B" box="[306,436,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="52">Berdeniella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
-like species but with two large tenacula of unequal size arranged in line on epandrial appendages; thorax and wings without characteristics; gonostyli longer than gonocoxites and markedly thinner in distal half; lateral sclerites of aedeagus with sharp tips, inner sclerites broad with apical edge serrate.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
